no-array-constructor.description:
Description

This rule disallowsArrayconstructors.

Examples ofincorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-array-constructor: "error"*/

Array();

Array(0, 1, 2);

new Array(0, 1, 2);

Array(...args);

Examples ofcorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-array-constructor: "error"*/

Array(500);

new Array(someOtherArray.length);

[0, 1, 2];

const createArray = Array => new Array();

This rule additionally supports TypeScript type syntax.

Examples ofcorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-array-constructor: "error"*/

new Array<number>(1, 2, 3);

new Array<Foo>();

Array<number>(1, 2, 3);

Array<Foo>();

Array?.foo();

Examples ofincorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-array-constructor: "error"*/

new Array();

new Array(0, 1, 2);

Array?.(x, y);

Array?.(0, 1, 2);
